{"id":579559,"date":[{"year":1979,"month":5,"day":28}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"487","ytitle":"","mtitle":"三十年巨变","ftitle":"——纪念上海解放三十周年","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>象是一颗明珠，镶在祖国的东大门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉映着天翻地覆三十春。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>江水和土地、主权，全被拍卖一空，屈辱和苦痛，深埋在旧上海的胸中……</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>百里海港，大吊巍巍云中走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——粮山煤海，稳稳托在手!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040104.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>扛不尽的苦呵扛不完的愁，一步步，“老杠棒”血汗洒遍旧码头!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040105.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>天真、可爱，用笑声追赶着彩球，　 ——美好的人生呵才开头!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040106.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>失去了童年，失去了自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼小的心灵中，留下的唯有恨和仇!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040107.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>放眼看，蓝天、白云、绿树中，一幢幢新村大楼展新容。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040108.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>遮不了雨，避不了风，苦与穷，连着飘摇的“滚地龙”。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040109.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>齿轮飞转人欢笑，争上游，月月创出高指标!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040110.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>进厂如进鬼门关，多少人，累断了脊骨累弯了腰?!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040111.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>琳琅满目呵任选购，乐陶陶，商场内外笑声留!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040112.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>捧着成捆“金圆券”，心中几多愁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买什么?一家老小难糊口……</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040113.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>“四化”的美景叫人醉呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹们，欢声笑语飞出嘴……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗达成、孙愚配诗</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>徐大刚,陈根宝,张鸿,臧志成,周学忠,罗达成,孙愚配</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040114.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>抽的是丝，抽的是血——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗心，年年月月泡苦水!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040115.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>品尝着新生活的香甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人呵，在欢度幸福的晚年。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1979\\05\\795s040116.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>破衣褴衫，怎禁得风冷雪寒?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讨饭篮里，装的是无限辛酸。</FONT>"}]}